text: Mridula Mandhatasinh Jadeja (born 6 January 1991) is a Gujarati cricketer. She played for Saurashtra and West zone. She has played 1 First-class matches, 46 Limited over matches and 36 Women's Twenty20. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Saurashtra women cricketers Category:West Zone women cricketers Category:Living people
title: Mridula Jadeja
